{"aid": "igkp3smcq2e4p0", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 3, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "i6roqnlkmtw", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-16T07:21:24Z", "content": "<p>关于ucore-docs中对于中断和异常的描述我有两点不太懂&#xff0c;求各位指点。</p>\n<p>1.在92页&#xff0c;3.3.2小节最下面&#xff0c;提到“当调用Interrupt Gate时&#xff0c;Interrupt会被CPU自动禁止&#xff1b;而调用Trap Gate时&#xff0c;CPU则不会去禁止或打开中断&#xff0c;而是保留它原来的样子”</p>\n<p>应该如何理解这句话呢&#xff1f;“CPU自动禁止”是不是说Interrupt Gate是不能嵌套的&#xff0c;而Trap Gate处理过程中可以嵌套另一个异常或者中断&#xff1f;这是不是表明了Interrupt的优先级比Trap要高呢&#xff1f;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>2.关于练习6的描述“注意除了系统调用中断(T_SYSCALL)以外&#xff0c;其它中断均使用中断门描述符&#xff0c;权限为内核态权限&#xff1b;而系统调用中断使用异常&#xff0c;权限为陷阱门描述符”</p>\n<p>系统调用的权限这里写错了吧&#xff0c;感觉权限应该是用户态权限或者内核态权限二选一&#xff08;个人感觉也是内核态权限不知道对不对&#xff09;&#xff0c;权限应该和陷阱门描述符没关系吧。</p>\n<p></p>", "subject": "ucore-docs中断与异常的部分"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": [], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446634962084, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-03-16T08:03:02Z", "id": "i7bl39e8stg47n", "tag_endorse": [], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-16T08:03:02Z", "content": "<p>1. 所谓“自动禁止”&#xff0c;指的是CPU跳转到interrupt gate里的地址时&#xff0c;在将EFLAGS保存到栈上之后&#xff0c;清除EFLAGS里的IF位。在中断处理例程里&#xff0c;操作系统可以将EFLAGS里的IF设上来允许嵌套中断&#xff0c;但是必须在此之前做好处理嵌套中断的必要准备。interrupt gate和trap gate之间没有优先级之分&#xff0c;仅仅是CPU在处理中断时有不同的方法&#xff0c;供操作系统在实现时根据需要进行选择。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>2. 对照其它中断的说法&#xff0c;系统调用中断应该是“使用陷阱门描述符&#xff0c;权限为用户态权限”&#xff0c;谢谢指出&#xff01;</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-16T16:11:27Z", "id": "i7c2jdp5vdc3vd", "updated": "2015-03-16T16:11:27Z", "subject": "<p>对于第一点&#xff0c;已经把上述补充更新到了gitbook和<a href=\"https://github.com/objectkuan/ucore_docs/blob/master/lab1/lab1_3_3_2_interrupt_exception.md\">https://github.com/objectkuan/ucore_docs/blob/master/lab1/lab1_3_3_2_interrupt_exception.md</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>对于第二点&#xff0c;好像我之前已经改了练习6的描述&#xff0c;建议 看看 gitbook上的ucore_doc&#xff0c;或者git pull <a href=\"https://github.com/objectkuan/ucore_docs.git\">https://github.com/objectkuan/ucore_docs.git</a>  获得最新文档。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>非常感谢&#xff01;</p>\n<p>希望有问题多提出来&#xff0c;老师和助教也会持续改进文档&#xff01;</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 10, "bucket_name": "Week 3/15 - 3/21", "no_upvotes": 0, "children": [], "type": "followup"}], "type": "question", "unique_views": 73, "created": "2015-03-16T07:21:24Z", "id": "i7bjlq9k1so7gv", "no_answer": 0, "nr": 119, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "upvote_ids": [], "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "folders": ["lab1"], "bucket_order": 2, "change_log": [{"uid": "i6roqnlkmtw", "when": "2015-03-16T07:21:24Z", "data": "i7bjlq9ujlz7gw", "anon": "no", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "when": "2015-03-16T08:03:02Z", "data": "i7bl39ebgqa47o", "to": "i7bjlq9k1so7gv", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "when": "2015-03-16T16:11:27Z", "to": "i7bjlq9k1so7gv", "anon": "no", "type": "followup"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "tags": ["lab1", "student"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 0, "tag_good": []}}